original_title: Roy Rogers with Dale Evans: Vol. 7
overview: Ride the range with America's favorite cowpoke in four episodes of the "The Roy Rogers Show," including "Death Medicine," in which Roy and Dale must free a kidnapped diabetic man before he perishes for lack of an insulin injection. In "Ghost Town Gold," the bullets fly over a stash of coins; in "The Lady Killer," Roy must stop a ruthless banker who's killing ranchers to get their land; and in "The Big Chance," a crook inherits a large fortune.
title: Roy Rogers with Dale Evans: Vol. 7
